<div id="wrap">
<div id="left_col">
  <br><a href="/"><img src="http://picasion.com/gl/89/bFTz.gif"></a><br>
  <i>your travel companion to destinations across the globe</i><br><br>
  <menu>
    <menuitem><a href="/">Home</a></menuitem>
    <menuitem><a href="/destination_search">DestinationFinder™</a></menuitem>
    <menuitem><a href="/destinations">Dérive Destinations</a></menuitem>
    <menuitem>
      <% if session[:user] %>
      <a href=<%= user_path(User.find_by(username: session[:user])) %>>My Profile</a>
      <% else %>
      <a href="/users/new">Create Account</a>
      <% end %>
    </menuitem>
    <menuitem>
      <% if session[:user] %>
      <%= link_to "Logout", logout_path, method: "delete" %>
      <% else %>
      <a href=<%= login_path %>>Login</a>
      <% end %>
    </menuitem>
  </menu>
<div>
  <img src="<%= @random.image %>" style="width:600px;"><br>
  <figcaption><center><%= @random.city %>, <%= @random.country %> •  <%= link_to "Learn more", destination_path(@random.id) %></center>
</div>

  <p>At <i>Dérive</i>, we strive to provide you with a travel destination, specifically tailored to your needs. Once you build your user profile, <i>Dérive</i> will craft a curated list of desirable destinations for your next trip.
  <br><br>
  Would you rather perform a custom search instead? You can find our DestinationFinder™ <%= link_to "here", "/destination_search"%>. Additionally, you can browse all of our <i>Dérive-approved</i> destinations <%= link_to "here", destinations_path%>.
  <br><br>
  <strong>Have questions?</strong> Reach out to our <i>Dérive</i> Concierge who are waiting to answer your questions. <a href="mailto:p6doyle@outlook.com?subject=Dérive Inquiry" target="_blank">Email</a> us today.</p>
